VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT sessions\.NewCookieStore\s*\(\s*\[\]byte\s*\(\s*["'][^"']{1,15}["']\s*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:rand\.Read|crypto/rand|os\.Getenv|SecretKeyBase|config\. && MISSING:test|example|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Gorilla session stores initialized with short or hardcoded authentication keys.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Weak or Short Session Store Key.
